      "recording_attendee_id": "c6678864-c9f1-48a4-876a-e4e6239d02a7",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "everything else that we offer, you know, obviously with it being being holidays, um probably not a lot of time today or for the rest of the week. But I wanted to see if you might be open, jumping on a call next week with my partner Cameron to talk a little bit more about what we have going on and and what you guys have going on over at Trillium as well."
