      "start_time": 214.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "c6678864-c9f1-48a4-876a-e4e6239d02a7",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "Okay. Okay. Yeah, I actually I'm looking right now. Um and had noticed that yeah, you guys have talked, I think I actually sent you sent you an email. It's all coming back to me now. It's funny how that works. Um we talked at the end of september um and then yeah, it looks like you and Cameron had talked on october um and he had mentioned, You know, delaying billing until January and locking the full portfolio rate for two thousand and twenty-one So if that's something that that you guys might be interested obviously with holidays coming up and maybe um getting something rolling until January that's definitely still on the table. Um So just wanted to touch base and check in and see how things are going."
